        Tokyo Academic Park, 2-2-1 Aomi, Koto-ku, Tokyo 135-8630  Japan
      %ul.listMark
        %li
          3 minutes walk from "Fune-no-Kagakukan"station on&nbsp;
          %a{ href: 'http://www.yurikamome.co.jp/en/', target: '_blank' }
            "Yurikamome" line
        %li
          15 minutes walk from "Tokyo Teleport" station on&nbsp;
          %a{ href: 'http://www.twr.co.jp/', target: '_blank' }
            "Rinkai" line
